snippet.title: Discarnate: Locust - Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now on Steam

You are tasked by The Collector to find a painting that has been locked away in the depths of an abandoned house. The Collector does not care how you find it, he cares about results and confidentiality. DO NOT attract unwanted attention, DO NOT fail him. Good Luck.

Chance for a single winner to win at least $1000.

Be sure to read the rules, terms, and privacy policy.

Music Track: "Cry" by Sascha Ende is licensed under CC BY 4.0

#Discarnate #DiscarnateLocust
